videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins runs for 35 yards moving the Wildcats to the UTEP 28-yard line.
videos.headline: Dawkins' 35-yard dash puts Arizona in UTEP territory

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins fakes the run and throws a two-yard pass to J.J. Taylor for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Dawkins pass to Taylor puts Wildcats on board first

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins completes a 36-yard pass to Shun Brown for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Dawkins' deep pass to Brown gives Arizona 2 TD lead

videos.description: UTEP's Kavika Johnson fumbles on a run up the middle and is recovered by Colin Schooler at the UTEP 27-yard line.
videos.headline: UTEP's fumble gives Arizona ball inside the 30

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins runs up the middle for a five-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Dawkins TD dive pads Arizona's lead

videos.description: UTEP QB Zack Greenlee completes a pass to Terry Juniel for a 40-yard pass putting the Miners at the Arizona 15-yard line.
videos.headline: Greenlee hits Juniel for 40 yards; puts UTEP in the red zone

videos.description: UTEP QB Zack Greenlee connects with Tyler Batson for a nine-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Greenlee to Batson puts UTEP on the board

videos.description: Arizona's Colin Schooler intercepts Zack Greenlee and returns it to the UTEP 5-yard line.
videos.headline: Schooler's INT puts Arizona at UTEP's 5-yard line

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins' dives into the end zone for a three-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Dawkins' 2nd rush TD of night widens gap

videos.description: Arizona coach Rich Rodriguez breaks down Brandon Dawkins first half performance and how his young defense is performing.
videos.headline: Rodriguez: Dawkins is seeing the field well tonight

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins runs for 13 yards and his third touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Dawkins' 3rd rush TD of night continues Arizona's dominance

videos.description: UTEP QB Mark Torrez throws to Kavika Johnson who then throws to Walter Down for a 38-yard pass deep in Arizona's end.
videos.headline: UTEP's double pass moves Miners to Arizona six-yard line

videos.description: UTEP QB Mark Torrez fakes the hand off and runs around the corner and into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Torrez TD run gives UTEP 2nd TD of night

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins adds to his night on the ground and rushes for 34 yards.
videos.headline: Dawkins 34-yard rush continues dominance on ground

videos.description: Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins completes a pass for one-yard to Bryce Wolma, who dives across the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Dawkins to Wolma gives Arizona 7 TDs on night

videos.description: Arizona RB Nathan Tilford takes the handoff up the middle for a two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tilford powers it up middle, adding to Arizona's lead

videos.description: Arizona QB Rhett Rodriguez has the ball go through his hands and is recovered by UTEP's Joseph Pickney at the Arizona 47-yard line.
videos.headline: Arizona's bad snap gives UTEP ball at midfield

videos.description: Arizona coach Rich Rodriguez explains how he liked the competitiveness the team showed and how talks about his son getting to play at the end of the game.
videos.headline: Rodriguez: Like teams' competitiveness, got nice road win

videos.description: Adam Amin and Dusty Dvoracek break down Arizona QB Brandon Dawkins performance and how this will help Arizona going into conference play.
videos.headline: Dvoracek: 'Arizona needed this to build confidence at QB'
